#. type: Title =
#: guide/transaction-spec/calculations/rounding.adoc:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "Rounding"
msgstr "金額の丸め込み"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/calculations/rounding.adoc:6
msgid ""
"To minimize the risk of differences due to rounding, the following rules "
"apply:"
msgstr "丸めによる差異のリスクを最小限に抑えるため、以下のルールを適用します:"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: guide/transaction-spec/calculations/rounding.adoc:10
msgid "All document level amounts shall have no decimals for accounting"
msgstr "すべての文書レベルの金額には、経理上の理由で小数点以下の桁がないこと。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: guide/transaction-spec/calculations/rounding.adoc:11
msgid "Invoice line net amount shall be rounded"
msgstr "請求明細行の正味金額は丸められること。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: guide/transaction-spec/calculations/rounding.adoc:12
msgid ""
"Results from calculations involving already rounded amounts are not subject "
"to rounding, like payable amounts and total amounts included CT."
msgstr ""
"消費税を含む支払金額や合計金額のように、すでに丸め込みされた金額を含む計算結"
"果は丸め込みの対象にはならないこと。"

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/calculations/rounding.adoc:14
msgid ""
"Please also see <<Calculation>> for details on how to calculate the "
"different amounts."
msgstr "各金額の計算方法については、 <<Calculation>> を参照してください。"
